FROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM golang:1.24-bookworm@sha256:d7d795d0a9f51b00d9c9bfd17388c2c626004a50c6ed7c581e095122507fe1ab AS builder

ARG TARGETPLATFORM
ARG TARGETOS
ARG TARGETARCH
ARG TARGETVARIANT=""
ARG LDFLAGS

ENV GO111MODULE=on \
    CGO_ENABLED=0 \
    GOOS=${TARGETOS} \
    GOARCH=${TARGETARCH} \
    GOARM=${TARGETVARIANT}

COPY . /go/src/github.com/open-policy-agent/gatekeeper
WORKDIR /go/src/github.com/open-policy-agent/gatekeeper/cmd/gator

RUN go build -mod vendor -a -ldflags "${LDFLAGS}" -o /gator

FROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian12@sha256:3f2b64ef97bd285e36132c684e6b2ae8f2723293d09aae046196cca64251acac AS build
USER 65532:65532
COPY --from=builder --chown=65532:65532 /gator /gator
ENTRYPOINT ["/gator"]
